        "suggestedApproach": "Start with core/change-set.ts. Watch exports FileStatus, FileNecessity, FileSensitivity, FileInclusion. High-complexity files: core/change-set.ts, core/runstate.ts, workers/base.ts, core/coordinator.ts, core/verification-pipeline.ts, server/websocket.ts, core/project-memory.ts. Avoid known landmine: core/change-set.ts is a high-blast-radius area (6) with elevated complexity.. Risk is medium; keep edits narrow.",
